# CLAUDE.md — {{PREFIX}}-meta

The **coordination layer** for the `{{PREFIX}}-*` family: a meta repo that sits above several independent sibling projects. It exists so that an agent working here gets the *whole* picture across them at once, governed by shared norms — instead of editing one blind to the others.

It holds coordination docs, not project content. Each member is its own repo with its own lifecycle; this layer never holds their files.

> This layer follows the shared `*-meta` git ceremony — subject-only commits, no `Co-Authored-By`.

## The family

{{#同型}}
